David Cavill | Director, Business Intelligence 











 
David Cavill is the director of business intelligence of Asta Funding Inc. and has been with the company since 2002.  He has extensive experience in business analysis, financial analysis and reporting, operational support and business development.  Cavill has also been responsible for overseeing the company’s I.T. department and I.T. director since 2012.Cavill has over 20 years of experience working for major financial services companies including Prudential and CIT Group in their treasury divisions.​Cavill earned a bachelor’s degree in economics from the University of Central Florida and a MBA from Centenary College of New Jersey.  
 

























