Item 5.02    Departure of Directors or Certain Officers; Election of Directors;
Appointment of Certain Officers; Compensatory Arrangements of Certain Officers.
As of July 17, 2017, Patrick F. Preece is no longer employed as Chief Executive
Officer of Simia Capital, LLC, ("Simia") a wholly owned subsidiary of Asta
Funding, Inc.
On an interim basis, Mr. Gary Stern, Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and
President of Asta Funding, Inc. will undertake the responsibilities of Simia's
Chief Executive Officer.
