Minimum requirements

                                        To qualify for a small business loan, your business needs to be at least a year old. You should have revenues of $50,000 annually or $4,200 per month over the last three months. 3 
                                    


Get the Kabbage app

                                        Apply, use your funds and manage your account right from your phone with the Kabbage app. It's the best funding you can get with two thumbs.
                                    






